posting_body: ['YES, WE ARE OPEN!', 'CALL NOW TO SCHEDULE AN IN-PERSON TOUR!', 'OR LET US SHOW YOU THROUGH FACETIME!', 'Welcome to Boulders at Puget Sound, conveniently located in North Tacoma, WA near Route 16, I-705 and I-5.', 'At Boulders at Puget Sound, we pride ourselves on providing the best apartment living that Tacoma has to offer.', 'Choose from our selection of one, two, and three-bedroom apartments - here, every layout was designed to meet all of your apartment needs.', 'Convinced Boulders at Puget Sound is the right Tacoma apartment for you?', 'Apply online today!', ' APARTMENTS IN TACOMA, WA WITH UNMATCHED AMENITIES', 'Amenities Include:', 'Cable Ready', 'Basketball Court', 'Abundant Natural Light', 'Online Payments Available', '48-hour Maintenance Commitment', 'Dog Park', 'Corporate Leases Available Upon Request', 'Nine-Foot Ceilings', 'Private Balcony', 'Attached or Detached Garages', 'Extra Storage', 'Wooded Views', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
